OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife: 'Our children kept
OL,4,Chim going until the end'
OL,6,FRob Burrow's children "kept him going
OL,7,Funtil the end", his wife Lindsey has
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FLindsey Burrow told ITV's Lorraine
OL,11,Fprogramme it had been a "tough few
OL,12,Fweeks" following the death of the
OL,13,Frugby league legend.
OL,15,FBurrow died at the age of 41 earlier
OL,16,Fthis month after being diagnosed with
OL,17,Fmotor neurone disease (MND) in 2019.
