OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife: 'Our children kept
OL,4,Chim going until the end'
OL,6,FFollowing his diagnosis, he dedicated
OL,7,Fhis life to raising awareness of the
OL,8,Fcondition and fundraising for a
OL,9,Fspecialist MND centre in Leeds.
OL,11,FPraising her husband as an
OL,12,F"inspiration", Lindsey said he was a
OL,13,F"devoted family man" who "worshipped"
OL,14,Ftheir children, Macy, Maya and Jackson.
OL,16,F"He would enjoy spending time with the
OL,17,Fchildren and that's what he lived
OL,18,Ffor," she said.
OL,20,F"I think the children kept him going
OL,21,Fright until the end.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
