OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife: 'Our children kept
OL,4,Chim going until the end'
OL,6,F"He wouldn't give in until his final
OL,7,Fbreath but he fought a courageous
OL,8,Fbattle with MND and we're incredibly
OL,9,Fproud of him."
OL,11,FAsked how their children were coping,
OL,12,FLindsey said: "They're my priority and
OL,13,Fmaking sure they're supported through
OL,14,Ftheir grief.
OL,16,F"They're just incredibly proud of
OL,17,Ftheir dad and the legacy that he
OL,18,Fleaves," she added.
