OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife: 'Our children kept
OL,4,Chim going until the end'
OL,6,FBurrow spent his entire career with
OL,7,FLeeds Rhinos and on Friday, 21 June,
OL,8,Fhis former club paid an emotional
OL,9,Ftribute before the first home game
OL,10,Fsince his death.
OL,12,FThe sold-out Headingley stadium stood
OL,13,Ffor a minute silence before the match.
OL,15,FBurrow's name and the number seven he
OL,16,Fwore was painted on the pitch.
OL,18,FThe Rhinos also wore a special
OL,19,Ffundraising kit which had been
OL,20,Fdesigned by artist Cath Muir, who was
OL,21,Fdiagnosed with MND in 2014.
