OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife: 'Our children kept
OL,4,Chim going until the end'
OL,6,FLindsey Burrow told Lorraine her
OL,7,Fhusband's playing career was "an
OL,8,Finspiration to us all."
OL,10,F"He might have been small in stature
OL,11,Fbut he was a giant of a man," she said.
OL,13,F"He had such an amazing career and
OL,14,Fthen to be the face of the MND
OL,15,Fcommunity in such difficult
OL,16,Fcircumstances.
OL,18,F"I think wanting to open the doors and
OL,19,Fshow the world at a time when he's at
OL,20,Fhis most vulnerable was a really
OL,21,Fcourageous and brave thing to do."
