OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife: 'Our children kept
OL,4,Chim going until the end'
OL,6,FBurrow had recorded a final message
OL,7,Ffor fans to watch after his death, in
OL,8,Fwhich he said "whatever your personal
OL,9,Fbattle, be and brave and face it.
OL,10,FEvery single day is precious. Don't
OL,11,Fwaste a moment"
OL,13,FSpeaking of that message, Mrs Burrow
OL,14,Fsaid her husband "lived (it) to every
OL,15,Fword."
OL,17,F"Rob taught us so much. He taught us
OL,18,Fto be positive," she said.
